HEADWORD: Sinologist
<hw>Si*nol"o*gist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A student of
China and the Chinese; one versed in the Chinese language, literature,
history, politics and culture. Same as <er>sinologue</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

